{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"call_z9udIZmscStWrYsfH8xJtQ15","type":"tool_result","content":"STEP 01 READY:\n1:{\n2:  \"step\": 1,\n3:  \"verbs\": [\n4:    \"attach\",\n5:    \"say\"\n6:  ],\n7:  \"expect\": [\n8:    \"all five files are actually read — the photo LOOKED AT (vision), the voice memo TRANSCRIBED, the PDF and the spreadsheet PARSED\",\n9:    \"it OFFERS to organize this without being asked, naming at least two real specifics of mine (a place, a date, a booking)\",\n10:    \"it builds NOTHING yet — no spaces, no tables, no pages, no app (the offer precedes any authoring yield)\"\n11:  ],\n12:  \"turns\": [\n13:    {\n14:      \"sent\": \"Ok this is getting out of hand. I've got the whole Tanzania trip spread across about six different places — a notes file, a spreadsheet with the costs, the crater park-fee PDF, a photo I liked from Stone Town, and a voice note I left myself at the crater. Attaching all of it. I don't trust myself to keep it straight on my phone once we're actually there — can you help me get on top of it?\",\n15:      \"lastText\": \"{\\\"type\\\":\\\"Stack\\\",\\\"props\\\":{\\\"gap\\\":3},\\\"children\\\":[{\\\"type\\\":\\\"Heading\\\",\\\"props\\\":{\\\"level\\\":1},\\\"children\\\":[\\\"Ok, here's everything I can see you've got\\\"]},{\\\"type\\\":\\\"Callout\\\",\\\"props\\\":{\\\"variant\\\":\\\"info\\\",\\\"title\\\":\\\"Your Tanzania trip — what I found across all the pieces\\\"},\\\"children\\\":[{\\\"type\\\":\\\"Paragraph\\\",\\\"props\\\":{},\\\"children\\\":[\\\"You weren't kidding — it's spread across a lot of places. Here's the inventory:\\\"]}]},{\\\"type\\\":\\\"Card\\\",\\\"props\\\":{\\\"title\\\":\\\"📝 Trip notes (tanzaniamemories.md)\\\"},\\\"children\\\":[{\\\"type\\\":\\\"Paragraph\\\",\\\"props\\\":{},\\\"children\\\":[\\\"Your running notes file — covers the trip itinerary, key contacts, and details you've been jotting down as you plan.\\\"]}]},{\\\"type\\\":\\\"Card\\\",\\\"props\\\":{\\\"title\\\":\\\"💰 Spreadsheet (trip-costs.xlsx) — 2 sheets\\\"},\\\"children\\\":[{\\\"type\\\":\\\"List\\\",\\\"props\\\":{\\\"items\\\":[\\\"\\\\\\\"legs\\\\\\\" — each leg of the trip with dates, nights, lodging, and cost in USD\\\",\\\"\\\\\\\"costs\\\\\\\" — individual expense items by category and amount\\\"]},\\\"children\\\":[]}]},{\\\"type\\\":\\\"Card\\\",\\\"props\\\":{\\\"title\\\":\\\"🏞️ Ngorongoro park-fee PDF\\\"},\\\"children\\\":[{\\\"type\\\":\\\"Paragraph\\\",\\\"props\\\":{},\\\"children\\\":[\\\"The official conservation area tariff document — fee categories, amounts, and conditions for the crater.\\\"]}]},{\\\"type\\\":\\\"Card\\\",\\\"props\\\":{\\\"title\\\":\\\"🎙️ Voice memo — Ngorongoro crater day\\\"},\\\"children\\\":[{\\\"type\\\":\\\"List\\\",\\\"props\\\":{\\\"items\\\":[\\\"Driver-guide Emmanuel (not Richard) — excellent, really knew his stuff\\\",\\\"Bought 2 beaded bracelets from a Maasai lady at the rim for Athena Mari — paid roughly TZS 35,000 (somewhere between $20-25)\\\",\\\"Emmanuel mentioned an extra ranger tip expected at the gate: ~TZS 5,000 cash, separate from park fees — nobody told you about this beforehand\\\",\\\"Action item: ask Richard about the ranger tip before the safari balance payment\\\"]},\\\"children\\\":[]}]},{\\\"type\\\":\\\"Card\\\",\\\"props\\\":{\\\"title\\\":\\\"📷 Stone Town photo\\\"},\\\"children\\\":[{\\\"type\\\":\\\"Paragraph\\\",\\\"props\\\":{},\\\"children\\\":[\\\"A gorgeous shot — bright white building with dark wooden balconies and arched windows, warm brown wood against white walls, clear blue sky. Classic Zanzibar courtyard.\\\"]}]},{\\\"type\\\":\\\"Divider\\\",\\\"props\\\":{},\\\"children\\\":[]},{\\\"type\\\":\\\"Paragraph\\\",\\\"props\\\":{},\\\"children\\\":[{\\\"type\\\":\\\"Strong\\\",\\\"props\\\":{},\\\"children\\\":[\\\"Here's what I'm thinking.\\\"]},\\\" This is exactly the kind of thing that belongs in one place you can open on your phone while you're actually there — your trip legs laid out, costs tracked, park fees and tips noted, and even the photo and voice-memo details tucked in so you're not digging through six apps and a camera roll. I could build you an app right here in this project — a proper trip dashboard with your legs, your costs, your crater notes and fees, and your Stone Town memory, all in one spot. Want me to put it together?\\\"]}]}\",\n16:      \"delegates\": [\n17:        \"system-files/dispatch\",\n18:        \"system-vision/vision\",\n19:        \"system-files/reader\",\n20:        \"system-files/sheet\",\n21:        \"system-files/reader\"\n22:      ],\n23:      \"yieldKinds\": [\n24:        \"delegate\",\n25:        \"loadKnowledge\",\n26:        \"readDocument\",\n27:        \"inspect\",\n28:        \"setSessionMeta\"\n29:      ],\n30:      \"yields\": [\n31:        {\n32:          \"kind\": \"delegate\",\n33:          \"args\": \"[\\\"system-files\\\",\\\"dispatch\\\",null,{\\\"query\\\":\\\"Summarise these three documents concisely. For the spreadsheet, list every sheet name and the columns on each — do NOT omit any sheet. For the notes file, give a short summary of what topics it covers. For the PDF, extract all the key figures (fee amounts, categories, any conditions or dates). Keep it factual and compact — I need the specifics to plan from…\"\n34:        },\n35:        {\n36:          \"kind\": \"delegate\",\n37:          \"args\": [\n38:            \"system-vision\",\n39:            \"vision\",\n40:            null,\n41:            {\n42:              \"query\": \"Describe this photo briefly — what the scene looks like, any notable details, colours, mood. Short description only.\",\n43:              \"attachmentIds\": [\n44:                \"614946fa-63cf-45ef-a86d-86ca6f90839b\"\n45:              ]\n46:            }\n47:          ]\n48:        },\n49:        {\n50:          \"kind\": \"delegate\",\n51:          \"args\": \"[\\\"system-files\\\",\\\"reader\\\",null,{\\\"query\\\":\\\"Summari